Adds recharge delay/reload time to weapon cards for Eridian and non-Eridian weapons, adds recharge delay to shield cards, and removes the five-line limit on cards.

1.2.1 changes:
	Turned CDP into its own mod, hopefully reducing stutters.
	Fixed "Shield" showing up on item cards when it isn't supposed to.

1.2.0 changes:
	Fixed constraint text not appearing.
	Added an option to remove elemental text from item cards.
	Added an option to display item parts on item card. (by RedxYeti)

1.1.0 changes:
	Removed the five-line limit on cards and added a font size option.
	Added support for EWO.
	Added support for Jakobs Vendor Fix.